rks on a product with a clear impact in a market full of opportunities, and with a realistic approach.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "rtl", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": "rtl"}}	\N	\N	\N	Ballurh - a business intelligence platform for the retail, restaurant, and cafe sectors.	\N	Increase your sales, predict demand behaviors, and improve performance indicators by making data-driven growth decisions using the power of business intelligence technologies.	1197	en	776bee6e-d93a-475f-aa30-53d23438faa4	\N	\N	f
